00:03:28.540 --> 00:03:31.609
If the people in power run the country based
on their idea of the “good old days,”

00:03:31.609 --> 00:03:34.790
it’s very possible that a) they’ll omit
other people’s narratives if it doesn’t

00:03:34.790 --> 00:03:38.230
align with their agenda, b) they’re trying
to make the present like their past which

00:03:38.230 --> 00:03:43.600
is the opposite of how time works, and c)
it’s nostalgia for them, not for the good

00:03:43.600 --> 00:03:44.620
of the whole system.

00:03:44.620 --> 00:03:47.960
So, politically, historical nostalgia
isn’t a platform to rally behind.

